{
  "id": "6999a47be594cb2894db1a1d",
  "title": "歴史的仮名遣いローマ字綴り",
  "created": 1771676825,
  "updated": 1773757272,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6999a47be594cb2894db1a1d",
      "text": "歴史的仮名遣いローマ字綴り",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771676825,
      "updated": 1771676825
    },
    {
      "id": "6999a49900000000005dfb2a",
      "text": "歴史的仮名遣いを更にローマ字に書き換えて、見たことないはずなのになぜか読める言語を作りたい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771676825,
      "updated": 1771677130
    },
    {
      "id": "6999a53600000000005dfb2c",
      "text": " 歴史的仮名遣ひを更に Roma の字に書き換へて、見たことないはずなのになぜか読むる言語を作りたい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771676982,
      "updated": 1771679938
    },
    {
      "id": "6999a6fc00000000005dfb2e",
      "text": "  歴史的仮名 tukapiwo sarany Romano ziny kaky kapete, mitakotonaihanz nanony nazeka yoml 言語wo tukuritay",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771677437,
      "updated": 1771680888
    },
    {
      "id": "6999af1500000000005dfb33",
      "text": "  Liksidik gameŋ tukapiwo sarany Romano nziny kaky kapete, mitakotonaihanz nanony nazeka yoml gianguwo tukuritay.",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771679509,
      "updated": 1771681220
    },
    {
      "id": "6999af1500000000005dfb34",
      "text": "  いい感じの音読み資料がないので広東語のイェール式と閩南語を引っ張ってきた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771679510,
      "updated": 1771680188
    },
    {
      "id": "6999b34700000000005dfb39",
      "text": "   漢音を広東語で、呉音を閩南語で表すと良い感じになるかもしれない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771680584,
      "updated": 1771680608
    },
    {
      "id": "6999b36d00000000005dfb3a",
      "text": "   そもそも漢音と呉音の綴り方がわかればいいんだけど",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771680621,
      "updated": 1771680651
    },
    {
      "id": "6999b41700000000005dfb3b",
      "text": "  ローマの綴りはイタリア語",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771680792,
      "updated": 1771680806
    },
    {
      "id": "6999ab3800000000005dfb31",
      "text": " mitakotonaihanz のところでゴリゴリの膠着語らしさが出ている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771678521,
      "updated": 1771680545
    },
    {
      "id": "6999b32000000000005dfb38",
      "text": "  形態素に分けると mi-ta-koto-nai-hanz",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771680545,
      "updated": 1771680575
    },
    {
      "id": "6999b30f00000000005dfb37",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771680527,
      "updated": 1771680527
    },
    {
      "id": "6999b8d700000000005dfb41",
      "text": "短文を作文するためにいちいち辞書を引かなければならない感覚が新鮮というか外国語初心者感があって懐かしいというか、そんな気分だ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771682008,
      "updated": 1771682061
    },
    {
      "id": "6999ba5900000000005dfb43",
      "text": "\tめっちゃめんどくさい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771682393,
      "updated": 1771682398
    },
    {
      "id": "6999b8e500000000005dfb42",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771682022,
      "updated": 1771682022
    },
    {
      "id": "699bffae00000000000ce52f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831215,
      "updated": 1771831215
    },
    {
      "id": "699bffae00000000000ce530",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831215,
      "updated": 1771831215
    },
    {
      "id": "699bffaf00000000000ce531",
      "text": "源氏物語の原文を処理したほうが話が早い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831215,
      "updated": 1771831229
    },
    {
      "id": "699bffbc00000000000ce533",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831229,
      "updated": 1771831229
    },
    {
      "id": "699c00cd00000000000ce540",
      "text": "筆記体にすると結構さまになる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831502,
      "updated": 1771831520
    },
    {
      "id": "699c00e000000000000ce542",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/26eeab539113f5be1182801c3f6c0c55]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831521,
      "updated": 1771831710
    },
    {
      "id": "699c019d00000000000ce545",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831710,
      "updated": 1771831710
    },
    {
      "id": "699c011c00000000000ce544",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831580,
      "updated": 1771831580
    },
    {
      "id": "699c00ce00000000000ce541",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831502,
      "updated": 1771831502
    },
    {
      "id": "699bffbc00000000000ce534",
      "text": "Yinduɾe-no 御時-ny-ka, 女御(nyau-ŋo), 更衣(kau-yi) amata sambuɾapy tamapy-keɾu naka-ny, yito yamu-ŋoto-naky 際(kiwa)-ny-pa aɾanu-ŋa, suŋuɾe-te 時meky tamapu aɾy-keɾy. ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831229,
      "updated": 1771831755
    },
    {
      "id": "699c01ca00000000000ce546",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831755,
      "updated": 1771831755
    },
    {
      "id": "699c01ca00000000000ce547",
      "text": " Panzime-yoɾy 我-pa-to 思py 上ŋaɾy-tamapeɾu 御方ŋata, menzama-ʃiky monony otoʃime 嫉my-tamapu. ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831755,
      "updated": 1771831755
    },
    {
      "id": "699c01ca00000000000ce548",
      "text": "同nzy pondo, soɾe-yoɾy 下臈(ŋe-ɾau)-no 更衣-taty-pa, maʃite yasu-kaɾa-nzu. ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831755,
      "updated": 1771831755
    },
    {
      "id": "699c01ca00000000000ce549",
      "text": "朝夕-no 宮仕pe-ny tuke-te-mo, 人-no 心-wo nomy 動ka-ʃy, 恨my-wo 負pu 積moɾy-ny-ya aɾy-kemu, yito 篤(atu)-ʃiku naɾy-yuky, mono-心細ŋe-ny 里ŋaty-naɾu-wo, yiyo-yiyo aka-nzu apaɾe-naɾu mono-ny 思poʃy-te, 人-no soʃiɾy wo-mo ye-憚ɾaʃe-tamapa-nzu, 世-no tameʃy-ny-mo naɾy-nu-mbeky 御-motenaʃy-naɾy. ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831755,
      "updated": 1771831755
    },
    {
      "id": "699c01ca00000000000ce54a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831755,
      "updated": 1771831755
    },
    {
      "id": "699c01ca00000000000ce54b",
      "text": " 上達部(kamu-ndati-me), 上人(wuyem-bito) nandomo, ayinaku 目-wo 側(somba)metutu, 「yito mambayuky 人-no 御omboye-naɾy. ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831755,
      "updated": 1771831755
    },
    {
      "id": "699c01ca00000000000ce54c",
      "text": "唐土-ny-mo, kakaɾu 事-no 起koɾy-ny-koso, 世mo 乱ɾe, 悪ʃy-kaɾy-keɾe」to, yau-yau 天-no 下-ny-mo andiky-nau, 人-no mote-nayamy-ŋusa-ny naɾy-te, 楊貴妃-no 例mo 引ky 出ndetum-beku naɾy-yuku-ny, yito paʃita-naky-koto 多kaɾe-ndo, katanzike-naky 御心mbape-no taŋupy-naky-wo 頼my-ny-te manziɾapy-tamapu. ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831755,
      "updated": 1771831755
    },
    {
      "id": "699c01ca00000000000ce54d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831755,
      "updated": 1771831755
    },
    {
      "id": "699c01ca00000000000ce54e",
      "text": " 父-no 大納言-pa 亡ku-naɾy-te, 母北-no 方-namu yiniʃipe-no 人-no yoʃy-aɾu-ny-te, 親uty 具ʃy, saʃy-ataɾy-te 世-no omboye panayaka-naɾu 御方ŋata-ny-mo yitau 劣ɾa-nzu, nany-ŋoto-no 儀式-wo-mo motenaʃy-tamapy-keɾe-ndo, toɾy-tate-te pakambaka-ʃiky 後見-ʃina-keɾe-mba, 事-aɾu 時-pa, napo 拠ɾy 所-naku 心細ŋe-naɾy. ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831755,
      "updated": 1771831755
    },
    {
      "id": "699c01ca00000000000ce54f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831755,
      "updated": 1771831755
    },
    {
      "id": "699c01ca00000000000ce550",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831755,
      "updated": 1771831755
    },
    {
      "id": "699bffbc00000000000ce532",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771831229,
      "updated": 1771831229
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95234000000000087ad03",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752884,
      "updated": 1773752884
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95224000000000087ad01",
      "text": "文化庁の歴史的仮名遣い資料があったぞ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752868,
      "updated": 1773752892
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95249000000000087ad85",
      "text": "\t[現代仮名遣いは情報量を減らす]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752906,
      "updated": 1773752916
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95240000000000087ad04",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752896,
      "updated": 1773752896
    },
    {
      "id": "69b959c8000000000087ad89",
      "text": "y よりも j の方が i っぽくていいな",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773754825,
      "updated": 1773755098
    },
    {
      "id": "69b959c8000000000087ad8a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773754825,
      "updated": 1773754825
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad05",
      "text": "table:Rekisiteki Raumazi Tuduri",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752897,
      "updated": 1773754770
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad06",
      "text": " 音韻\t現仮名\t歴仮名\tRRT\t例",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773754763
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad07",
      "text": "　イ\tい\tい\ti\t石(isi)　赤(aka)i　意図(ito)　愛(ai)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753850
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9532a000000000087ad87",
      "text": "　\t\t\tji\t報(muku)j-ir-u",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773753130,
      "updated": 1773755553
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad08",
      "text": " 　\t\tゐ\twi\t井戸(wido)　居(wir, wor)-u　参(maw)-ir-u　胃(wi)　権威(kenwi)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756651
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad09",
      "text": " 　\t\tひ\tpi\t貝(kapi)　合図(apidu)　費(tupi)yas-u　思(omop)-i 出(de)　恋(kopi)-si-sa",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756669
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad0a",
      "text": " ウ\tう\tう\tu\t歌(uta)　馬(uma、muma)　浮(u)kabu　雷雨(raiu)　機運(kiun)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773754062
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad0b",
      "text": " 　\t\tふ\tpu\t買(kap)-u　吸(su)p-u　争(arasop, sumap)-u　危(aya)pu-i",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756747
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad0c",
      "text": " エ\tえ\tえ\te\t柄(e, gara)　枝(eda)　心得(kokoroe)　栄誉(eijo)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773754165
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95717000000000087ad88",
      "text": " \t\tえ(𛀁)\tje\t見(mi)j-er-u",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773754136,
      "updated": 1773755664
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad0d",
      "text": " 　\t\tゑ\twe\t声(kowe)　植(uw)-er-u　絵(we)　円(wen)　知恵(tiwe)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756756
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad0e",
      "text": " 　\t\tへ\tpe\t家(ipe)　前(mape)　考(kanga)p-er-u　帰(kap-er, kap-ir)-u　救(sukup)-e",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756790
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad0f",
      "text": " 　\tへ\tへ\tpe\t西(nisi) pe 進(susu)m-u",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773755745
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad10",
      "text": " オ\tお\tお\to\t奥(oku)　大人(otona)　起(o)k-ir-u　o話(panas-i)　雑音(zatuon)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756806
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad11",
      "text": " 　\t\tを\two\t男(wotoko)　十日(towoka)　踊る(wodor-u)　青い(awo-i)　悪寒(wokan)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773755782
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad12",
      "text": " 　\t\tほ\tpo\t顔(kapo)　氷(kopor-i)　滞(todokopor)-u　直(napos)-u　大(opo)ki-i",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756854
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad13",
      "text": " 　\t\tふ\tpu\t仰(apug)-u　倒(tapur)-er-u",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756869
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad14",
      "text": " 　\tを\tを\two\t花(pana) wo 見(m)-ir-u",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756902
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad15",
      "text": " カ\tか\tか\tka\t蚊(ka)　紙(kami)　静(siduk)-a　家庭(katei, yanipa)　休暇(kiuka)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756919
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad16",
      "text": " 　\t\tくわ\tkwa\t火事(kwazi)　歓迎(kwangei)　結果(ketkwa)　生活(seikwatu, sjaukwatu)　愉快(jukwai)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773755013
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad17",
      "text": " ガ\tが\tが\tga\t石垣(isigaki)　学問(gakumon)　岩石(ganseki)　生涯(sjaugai)　発芽(patuga)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773755378
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad18",
      "text": " 　\t\tぐわ\tgwa\t画家(gwaka)　外国(gwaikoku)　丸薬(gwanjaku)　正月(sjaugwatu)　念願(nengwan)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773755023
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad19",
      "text": " ジ\tじ\tじ\tzi\t初(pazi)m-e　kozi-開(a)k-er-u　字(zi)　自慢(ziman)　術語(zjutugo)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773755959
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad1a",
      "text": " 　\t\tぢ\tdi\t味　恥d-ir-u　地面　女性　正直",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773755970
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad1b",
      "text": " 　\tぢ\tぢ\tdi\t縮m-u　鼻血　底力　近々　入れ知恵",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773755980
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad1c",
      "text": " ズ\tず\tず\tzu\t鈴　物好き　知らずに　人数　洪水",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753295
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad1d",
      "text": " 　\t\tづ\tdu\t水　珍しい　一 tu dutu　図画　大豆",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773755990
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad1e",
      "text": " 　\tづ\tづ\tdu\t鼓　続く　三日月　塩漬け　常々",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753300
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad1f",
      "text": " ワ\tわ\tわ\twa\t輪　泡　声色　弱い　和紙",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753304
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad20",
      "text": " 　\t\tは\tpa\t川　回る　思p-a zu　柔raka　琵*琶*（bipa）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756003
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad21",
      "text": " 　\tは\tは\tpa\t我 pa 海 no 子　又 pa",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756016
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad22",
      "text": " ユー\tゆう\tゆう\tyuu\t勇気　英雄　金融",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753314
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad23",
      "text": " 　\t\tゆふ\tyupu\t夕方",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753318
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad24",
      "text": " 　\t\tいう\tiu\t遊戯　郵便　勧誘　所有",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753321
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad25",
      "text": " 　\t\tいふ\tipu\t都邑*(tipu)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756032
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad26",
      "text": " 　\tいう\tいふ\tipu\t言p-u",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756064
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad27",
      "text": " オー\tおう\tおう\tou\t負-u te　応答　欧米",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756047
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad28",
      "text": " 　\t\tあう\tau\t桜花　奥義　中央",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753335
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad29",
      "text": " 　\t\tあふ\tapu\t扇　押収　凹凸",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753337
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad2a",
      "text": " 　\t\tわう\twau\t弱-u　王子　往来　卵黄",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756073
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad2b",
      "text": " 　\t\tはう\tpau\t買p-a u　舞p-a u　怖u goza-i masu",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756117
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad2c",
      "text": " コー\tこう\tこう\tkou\t功績　拘束　公平　気候　振興",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753347
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad2d",
      "text": " 　\t\tこふ\tkopu\t劫* (kopu)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756134
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad2e",
      "text": " 　\t\tかう\tkau\t咲k-a u　赤-u　kau si te　講義　健康",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756169
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad2f",
      "text": " 　\t\tかふ\tkapu\t甲乙　太閤*(taikapu)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756211
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad30",
      "text": " 　\t\tくわう\tkwau\t光線　広大　恐慌　破天荒",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753359
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad31",
      "text": " ゴー\tごう\tごう\tgou\t皇后",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753363
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad32",
      "text": " 　\t\tごふ\tgopu\t業　永劫*(eigopu)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756222
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad33",
      "text": " 　\t\tがう\tgau\t急がう　長う　強引　豪傑　番号",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753368
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad34",
      "text": " 　\t\tがふ\tgapu\t合同",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753374
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad35",
      "text": " 　\t\tぐわう\tgwau\t轟*音(gwauon)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773757030
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad36",
      "text": " ソー\tそう\tそう\tsou\t僧　総員　競争　吹奏　放送",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753383
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad37",
      "text": " 　\t\tさう\tsau\t話s-a u　浅 u　sau si te　草案　体操",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756266
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad38",
      "text": " 　\t\tさふ\tsapu\t挿話",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753389
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad39",
      "text": " ゾー\tぞう\tぞう\tsou\t増加　憎悪　贈与",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753393
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad3a",
      "text": " 　\t\tざう\tzau\t象　蔵書　製造　内臓　仏像",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753396
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad3b",
      "text": " 　\t\tざふ\tzapu\t雑煮",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753399
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad3c",
      "text": " トー\tとう\tとう\ttou\t弟　統一　冬至　暴投　北東",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753402
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad3d",
      "text": " 　\t\tたう\ttau\t峠　勝t-a u　痛-u　刀剣　砂糖",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756300
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad3e",
      "text": " 　\t\tたふ\ttapu\t塔　答弁　出納",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753408
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad3f",
      "text": " ドー\tどう\tどう\tdou\tdou si te　銅　童話　運動　空洞",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756311
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad40",
      "text": " 　\t\tだう\tdau\t堂　道路　葡*萄*(budau)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756321
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad41",
      "text": " 　\t\tだふ\tdapu\t問答",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753415
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad42",
      "text": " ノー\tのう\tのう\tnou\t能　農家　濃紺",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753418
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad43",
      "text": " 　\t\tのふ\tnopu\t昨日",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753421
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad44",
      "text": " 　\t\tなう\tnau\t死n-a u　危n-au goza-i masu　脳　苦悩",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756354
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad45",
      "text": " 　\t\tなふ\tnapu\t納入",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753428
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad46",
      "text": " ホー\tほう\tほう\tpou\t奉祝　俸給　豊年　霊峰",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753446
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad47",
      "text": " 　\t\tほふ\tpopu\t法会",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753451
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad48",
      "text": " 　\t\tはう\tpau\t葬る　包囲　芳香　解放",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753454
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad49",
      "text": " 　\t\tはふ\tpapu\thapur-i 投ger-u　papupapu no 体　法律",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756413
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad4a",
      "text": " ボー\tぼう\tぼう\tbou\t某　貿易　解剖　無謀",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753464
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad4b",
      "text": " 　\t\tぼふ\tbopu\t正法",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753467
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad4c",
      "text": " 　\t\tばう\tbau\t遊b-a u　飛b-a u　紡績　希望　堤防",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756434
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad4d",
      "text": " 　\t\tばふ\tbapu\t貧乏",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753474
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad4e",
      "text": " ポー\tぽう\tぽう\tpou\t本俸　連峰",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753480
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad4f",
      "text": " 　\t\tぽふ\tpopu\t説法",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753483
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad50",
      "text": " 　\t\tぱう\tpau\t鉄砲　奔放　立方",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753486
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad51",
      "text": " 　\t\tぱふ\tpapu\t立法",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753489
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad52",
      "text": " モー\tもう\tもう\tmou\tmou 一 tu　啓蒙*(keimou)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756456
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad53",
      "text": " 　\t\tまう\tmau\t申s-u　休m-a u　甘-u　猛獣　本望",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756472
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad54",
      "text": " ヨー\tよう\tよう\tyou\t見j-o u　jou goza-i masu　用　容易　中庸",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756509
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad55",
      "text": " 　\t\tやう\tyau\t八日　早う　様子　洋々　太陽",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753560
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad56",
      "text": " 　\t\tえう\teu\t幼年　要領　童謡　日曜",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753562
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad57",
      "text": " 　\t\tえふ\tepu\t紅葉",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753565
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad58",
      "text": " ロー\tろう\tろう\trou\t楼　漏電　披露",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753568
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad59",
      "text": " 　\t\tろふ\tropu\tkageropu 　pukuropu",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756533
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad5a",
      "text": " 　\t\tらう\trau\t祈r-a u　暗-a u　廊下　労働　明朗",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756563
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad5b",
      "text": " 　\t\tらふ\trapu\t候文　蝋*燭*(rapusoku)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773756559
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad5c",
      "text": " キョー\tきょう\tきよう\tkjou\t共通　恐怖　興味　吉凶",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753622
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad5d",
      "text": "　\t\tきやう\tkjau\t兄弟　鏡台　経文　故郷　熱狂",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753621
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad5e",
      "text": "　\t\tけう\tkeu\t教育　矯正　絶叫　鉄橋",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753594
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad5f",
      "text": "　\t\tけふ\tkepu\t今日　脅威　協会　海峡",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753596
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad60",
      "text": "　ギョー\tぎょう\tぎよう\tgjou\t凝集",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753619
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad61",
      "text": "　\t\tぎやう\tgjau\t仰天　修行　人形",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753618
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad62",
      "text": "　\t\tげう\tgeu\t今暁",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753609
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad63",
      "text": "　\t\tげふ\tgepu\t業務",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753613
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad64",
      "text": "　ショー\tしょう\tしよう\tsjou\t昇格　承諾　勝利　自称　訴訟",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753634
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad65",
      "text": "　\t\tしやう\tsjau\t詳細　正直　商売　負傷　文章",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753638
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad66",
      "text": "　\t\tせう\tseu\t見-i mase u　小説　消息　少年　微笑",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773757120
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad67",
      "text": "　\t\tせふ\tsepu\t交渉",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753645
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad68",
      "text": "　ジョー\tじょう\tじよう\tzjou\t冗談　乗馬　過剰",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753657
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad69",
      "text": "　\t\tじやう\tzjau\t成就　上手　状態　感情　古城",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753662
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad6a",
      "text": "　\t\tぜう\tzeu\t饒*舌(zeuzetu)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773757143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad6b",
      "text": "　\t\tぢやう\tdjau\t定石　丈夫　市場　令嬢",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753671
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad6c",
      "text": "　\t\tでう\tdeu\t箇条",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753673
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad6d",
      "text": "　\t\tでふ\tdepu\t一帖*(itidepu)　六畳",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773757151
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad6e",
      "text": "　\tぢょう\tぢやう\tdjau\t盆提△灯△(bondjautin)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773757177
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad6f",
      "text": "　\t\tでう\tdeu\t一本調子",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753684
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad70",
      "text": "　チョー\tちょう\tちよう\ttjou\t徴収　清澄　尊重",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753693
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad71",
      "text": "　\t\tちやう\ttjau\t腸　町会　聴取　長短　手帳",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753697
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad72",
      "text": "　\t\tてう\tteu\t調子　朝食　弔電　前兆　野鳥",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753700
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad73",
      "text": "　\t\tてふ\ttepu\t蝶*(tepu)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773757187
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad74",
      "text": "　ニョー\tにょう\tによう\tnjou\t女房",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753708
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad75",
      "text": "　\t\tねう\tneu\t尿",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753711
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad76",
      "text": "　ヒョー\tひょう\tひよう\tpjou\t氷山",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753715
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad77",
      "text": "　\t\tひやう\tpjau\t拍子　評判　兵糧",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753719
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad78",
      "text": "　\t\tへう\tpeu\t表裏　土俵　投票",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753721
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad79",
      "text": "　ビョー\tびょう\tびやう\tpjau\t病気　平等",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753725
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad7a",
      "text": "　\t\tべう\tpeu\t秒読m-i　描写",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773757228
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad7b",
      "text": "　ピョー\tぴょう\tぴよう\tpjou\t結氷　信憑*性(sinpjou-sei）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773757216
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad7c",
      "text": "　\t\tぴやう\tpjau\t論評",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753735
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad7d",
      "text": "　\t\tぺう\tpeu\t一票　本表",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753738
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad7e",
      "text": "　ミョー\tみょう\tみやう\tmjau\t名代　明日　寿命",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753742
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad7f",
      "text": "　\t\tめう\tmjeu\t妙技",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753746
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad80",
      "text": "　リョー\tりょう\tりよう\trjou\t丘陵",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753749
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad81",
      "text": "　\t\tりやう\trjau\t領土　両方　善良　納涼　分量",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753753
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad82",
      "text": "　\t\tれう\treu\t寮　料理　官僚　終了",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753757
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad83",
      "text": "　\t\tれふ\trepu\t漁　猟",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773753760
    },
    {
      "id": "69b95241000000000087ad84",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773752898,
      "updated": 1773752898
    },
    {
